  "description": "<i>Mystic Defender</i> is a side-scrolling platform game. It is the sequel to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/spellcaster\">SpellCaster</a> for the Sega Master System. However, in this sequel the RPG elements have been omitted in favour of side-scrolling platform gameplay.<br><br>In this game you play Joe Yamata (Kujaku) on a quest to rescue Alexandra from the villainous Zao, who is using her soul to resurrect his master Zareth in Azuchi castle. You have four types of magic to attack with and you can charge your blasts as well as change the magic type mid-game. ",
